  category    = {active_project},
  abstract    = {An ongoing randomized controlled trial of an established 8-week baby sign language curriculum, examining effects on caregiver-child bonding, caregiver responsiveness, and child language and socio-emotional development. Currently in design and partner-recruitment phase, in collaboration with community partners in Houston, TX.}
